    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as your best friend? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for road trips or just zipping around town! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for its next big adventure with a new owner. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
